(Next up: ICL health centre.) 
We are also not planning to take over the world with killer robots.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies and installation instructions
---------------------------------------------------------------------

nltk      : http://nltk.org/install.html
nltk_data : http://nltk.org/data.html

---------------------------------------------------------------------
How to run the script
---------------------------------------------------------------------

python angela.py
